assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Polynet Public Company Limited produces and sells rubber, plastic, and silicone related products in Thailand. The company offers rubber and plastic products for the automotive industry comprising airbag cover, harness and silicone valve, air filter, air delivery joint, dustproof rubber, stable rubber, ductile iron, and shaft sleeve, rubber dust brake, exhaust hanger, bumper, conduit, rubber pad, door, and fender. It also provides silicone resin and plastic components, including silicone sleeve, silicone valve, silicone hose and breathing hose, nasal intubation, sperm conductor, oxygen mask, sanitary cup, and medical equipment parts for the medical devices industry; and rubber on the surface of basketball and packaging rubber seals, bulb rubber seals, silicone food bags, the steam drain of a rice cooker, tea strainer, bottle cover and food box cover, etc., for consumer products industry. The company also exports its products to the United States, Japan, Indonesia, and Malaysia. Polynet Public Company Limited was founded in 1999 and is headquartered in Bang Sao Thong, Thailand.
